Need help sleeping at night?  Maybe a few moments of meditative peace?  Sleepwords will help you.  Random object names pass in front of you to help clear your mind of annoying thoughts and turn your mind off.

FEATURES
* Sleep mode - will turn off after a set period of time
* Control the speed of the words
* Control if their placement is random or in the center of the screen


Promo text:
Help your mind find relaxation